
---

### 3. Create `.gitignore`

Create a file named `.gitignore` and add this:

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python
env/
venv/
ENV/
build/
develop-eggs/
dist/
downloads/
eggs/
.eggs/
lib/
lib64/
parts/
sdist/
var/
wheels/
*.egg-info/
.installed.cfg
*.egg

# Local environment variables and credentials
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx

# Logs
stove_calculations_log.csv
*.log

# Sensitive
.env
.env.*
secrets.json
credentials.json

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/

# Node
node_modules/
package-lock.json
**/node_modules/
**/package-lock.json
